des:
Calculate 24 is a math puzzle game. For each question, I will give you 4 numbers and your goal is to calculate these numbers and come out a final result of 24.
-You have to use each number one time;
-You can use operation like plus, minus, times and divide;

The game has 2 modes. You can improve your skill in Practice game. Say tell me the answer and I will tell you the answer. In challenge game, you need to give right answers to 3 questions. Say skip if you don't want to be stuck at a question. You can skip up to 3 question in a challenge game. You compete with others for who can finish 3 questions with the shortest time.
